Package: COBRA
Type: Package
Title: COrrection of BAtch Effect for Single-Cell RNA-Seq Data
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Sujin", "Seo", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "sujin91kr@gmail.com")
Description: Removes unwanted batch variation from single-cell RNA-seq
    expression matrices while preserving biological signal. Batch effects
    are estimated via orthogonal projection of batch-related design matrix
    columns after partialling out biological covariates. When cell-type
    annotations are unavailable, pseudo-cell types are inferred
    automatically through iterative clustering on PCA-reduced space with
    elbow-based dimensionality selection.
